### How to work with us

Given the number groups this team supports, we prefer to be aware of upcoming features as early as possible. During the time leading up to implementation we will strive to:

1. Understand the problem we are trying to solve.
1. Collaborate with the appropriate Backend team, Product Management and UX to identify an achievable MVC.
1. Work with the various Product Managers we support to understand relative priority.

We seek to have issues ready for backlog refinement activities by the 1st of each month, therefore allowing enough time for us to determine the 
appropriate implementation plan and finalize relative sizing of the candidate issues in a given release.

